name: Depleting 20's
description:
We are completing 2 x 5min Sub-threshold intervals and 6 x 20sec accelerations. However, with the 20sec accelerations coming after the first 5min Sub-threshold interval, we aim to deplete your intramuscular glycogen stores and see what effect this has on the second 5min interval.
